doc.after: Specialized multi mission aircraft provide support for global special operations missions These aircraft conduct infiltration exfiltration resupply and refueling for SOF teams from improvised or otherwise short runways The MC 130J is currently being fielded to replace H and P models used by U S Special Operations Command The MC 12W is used in the Intelligence Surveillance and Reconnaissance ISR role
